questions.quote: Ok, well, alright, who thinks the food is fine, the music was fine, but your evening was ruined by this incessant poll taking? .
You know how much I love that T-shirt! You never even where that T-shirt!
No, you don't have to, and you can't because I live here too.
Yeah, oh, Princess Leia and the gold bikini, every guy our age loved that.
Oh, look at these! Hey, Ben. Just do it. Oh my God, oh, ok, was that too much pressure for him?
Well not when they find out you slept with Jason Hurley an hour after he broke up with Monica.
Okay, well, if she always behaves like this, why don't you say something?
I'm not gonna gooo, so I think that will accomplish the not going.
See, I told you I needed someone! Oh, you know, by the way, as a "thank you", I would really love to take you out.
Okay. But wait, we can't. My Cousin Cassie is in the guest room, we're supposed to have lunch.
